    {
        "content": "<p>Aha! I am able to get it working in the original if-then-else form using</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">repeat'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">split</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">simp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"m\">2</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"m\">2</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Thank you!</p>",
